(116,	1,	'2018-11-03 02:34:53',	'2018-11-03 02:34:53',	'Pushing women to the forefront, Her Sound, Her Story is an intimate conversation unveiling the personal experiences, histories and the significant social impact women have within the Australian music industry. Featuring conversations with over forty women this one-of-a-kind all-female narrative is brimming with individuality, strength and creativity.  This bold, unflinching take on the issues at heart extends beyond music industry, and asks “where do we want women’s voices to sit in the world today?”\r\n\r\nBeloved artists including Tina Arena, Jen Cloher and Mojo Juju discuss their personal journeys as they reflect on their collective and unspoken struggles of being a women in a male dominant industry. Hopeful in the prospect that change is on the horizon, and focused on the potent time to inspire the future generations to come.',	'Her Sound Her Story',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'her-sound-her-story',	'',	'',	'2018-11-03 02:34:53',	'2018-11-03 02:34:53',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:3157/raspberry/?post_type=event&#038;p=116',	0,	'event',	'',	0),
