(118,	1,	'2018-11-03 02:36:23',	'2018-11-03 02:36:23',	'A story of true life challenge and triumph, a group of young women take the stage with a fierceness – with each move it seems that they are putting everything on the line, because they are. They are teenagers on the verge of womanhood, by turns graceful, goofy, joyous, determined, elegant, insecure, hopeful but always passionate. These are the Lethal Ladies of The Baltimore Leadership School for Young Women (BLSYW), and they are not only a competitive step team headed for a multi-state showdown but are also aiming to break barriers as the first graduates of their school, whose mission is to send every single one of its students to college.',	'Step',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'step',	'',	'',	'2018-11-03 02:36:23',	'2018-11-03 02:36:23',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:3157/raspberry/?post_type=event&#038;p=118',	0,	'event',	'',	0),
